divs: Sighting Detailsi was driving home from a meeting noticed a orange dot in the sky that didnt look like an airplane. at first i thought it was a rocket but it didnt move like one. its stayed at one level in sky and did not move higher. then as i watched it it changed from orange to a more white color. it was there and when i got off the interstate my view was cut off by some trees and when i looked again it was gone. no strange feelings at all.
